{"tid":965291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【腰骨有事？巴士客癱坐關愛座　向乘客大Show波鞋】","createTime":"2019-01-02T02:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T06:50:59.000Z","uid":225464,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"df680424bb482ca3f989675e309de1c8660f6a87","tid":965291,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T02:30:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190102/bkn-20190102101138927-0102_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190102%2Fbkn-20190102101138927-0102_00822_001.html&d=0H%2Friwu7FwwZDgfqMGtu84zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=b3f12aca\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190102/bkn-20190102101138927-0102_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3jxGCMa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3jxGCMa.jpg&h=2d816a7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>腰骨有事？巴士客癱坐關愛座　向乘客大Show波鞋</strong><br />\n<br />\n關愛座原意是讓座予殘疾人士、孕婦、老人或有需要人士等，但近日有巴士乘客坐在關愛座上，竟然能施展「軟骨功」，將雙腳晾在扶手上，令一眾網民嘖嘖稱奇。<br />\n<br />\n照片於周日（30日）上載至Facebook專頁「大埔友」，只見有巴士乘客坐在關愛座上，以「癱坐」的姿勢玩手機，並在扶手上將雙腳上的白色波鞋「展示」於其他乘客的眼前。<br />\n<br />\n大批網民見狀狂派嬲：「廢柴」、「無脊椎動物」、「簡直不知所謂」，有人戲言：「落車嘅時候，除咗佢隻鞋掉去對面馬路」、「好想巴士急停」。"},{"pid":"a53bfab25d8080be029d76afab5966c227070ba5","tid":965291,"uid":34223,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T02:35:49.000Z","msg":"第一眼係睇到向乘客show大波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a68eadd163eb399e4510e90a3aeed066ded1b88","tid":965291,"uid":8392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T03:06:12.000Z","msg":"咁坐都唔舒服啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4961377947e9fc2bac8153bc3360621e55d0a057","tid":965291,"uid":176442,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T03:10:08.000Z","msg":"殘廢坐關愛座有乜問題？"},{"pid":"e75c7960a1e2c6fedc8f07b53306bae75dd9923c","tid":96529